title: Lifetime-Taken For Ransom [2013]

Lifetime-Taken for Ransom [2013]

Air Date 29 Dec 2013

Summary: A wealthy high powered woman suffers a horrible tragedy after which she descends into substance abuse, turning her back on her family. She later discovers that someone close to her may be behind her subsequent abduction and kidnapping.
